dc_title_s: Sustainable Community Areas: Anne Arundel County, Maryland
dc_description_s: The Glen Burnie and Brooklyn Park Sustainable Community Boundaries were created as part of an application to the State for designation as Sustainable Communities per the Sustainable Communities Act of 2010 (HB 475), which consolidated all previously DHCD-designated Community Legacy Areas and Designated Neighborhoods. As part of its application for designation, the County adopted this boundary in Glen Burnie by County Resolution 49-13 and adopted the Brooklyn Park boundary by County Resolution 28-13.Odenton-Severn Sustainable Community. Odenton-Severn Sustainable Community approved by MD DHCD in 2014
